<subSubSection id="C35E653A1F08FFC8279DF87BFB22F78C" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="8BFB36B11F08FFC8279DF87BFDB9F86F" blockId="13.[136,1452,1973,2072]" pageId="13" pageNumber="286">
<emphasis id="B930EAA31F08FFC8279DF87BFE9FF854" bold="true" box="[189,294,1973,1999]" pageId="13" pageNumber="286">Ecology:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="4C444D321F08FFC82662F87BFD90F854" box="[322,553,1973,1999]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Psephellus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="poluninii">
<emphasis id="B930EAA31F08FFC82662F87BFD90F854" box="[322,553,1973,1999]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="286">Psephellus poluninii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is an Irano-Turanian element, and grows on scree slopes in the high-montane zone, at elevations of ca. 
<quantity id="4CBC9B541F08FFC82684F817FE45F86F" box="[420,508,2009,2036]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.3" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="m" value="3300.0">3300 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BFB36B11F08FFC8279DF833FB22F78C" blockId="13.[136,1452,1973,2072]" box="[189,1179,2045,2072]" pageId="13" pageNumber="286">
